    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Demo只开放一张地图—长生苑，玩家可以体验到游戏的大部分机制和玩法。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你将扮演立场、使命和战斗方式各不相同的6位角色中的一位，潜入“断臂”残垣、波谲云诡的大秦都城咸阳，在这个架空历史的武侠朋克世界中探索、收集、战斗、成长。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332750/extras/6d9031024f76c40f5e08a31136c23f38.avif?t=1770106220\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332750/extras_big/6d9031024f76c40f5e08a31136c23f38.avif?t=1770106220 width=800 height=111 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你需要在36个时辰的时限里合理规划探索的建筑和顺序，每个建筑的环境和内容都有可能根据时间和一些世界事件的触发而发生变化。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332750/extras/424082d7202edbd0e3b1c49990aaecaa.poster.avif?t=1770106220\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332750/extras/424082d7202edbd0e3b1c49990aaecaa.webm?t=1770106220\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332750/extras/d96b05a4e1121ae055d70f21f2d29f96.avif?t=1770106220\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332750/extras_big/d96b05a4e1121ae055d70f21f2d29f96.avif?t=1770106220 width=800 height=111 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >正面决斗？潜行暗杀？借刀杀人？不战而胜？面对初入房间、盖在场上的一张张敌人生物卡牌，你可以根据你的卡组构筑和房间环境，自由选择如何解决他们。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332750/extras/97a72bad26270dd4b920a3f317a5b03a.poster.avif?t=1770106220\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332750/extras/97a72bad26270dd4b920a3f317a5b03a.webm?t=1770106220\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的卡组中除了战斗行为外，也包含可在战斗外使用的各式“物品牌”和“探索牌”，它们将助你破解机关、改变环境、寻宝探秘以及与咸阳城内的角色们对话沟通。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332750/extras/a56caa3fe3c06f5986f0773fbf84c2ee.poster.avif?t=1770106220\" width=800 height=640 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332750/extras/a56caa3fe3c06f5986f0773fbf84c2ee.webm?t=1770106220\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332750/extras/b772a43c15ce1a58b279677763833515.avif?t=1770106220\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332750/extras_big/b772a43c15ce1a58b279677763833515.avif?t=1770106220 width=800 height=111 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你在战斗中的行动牌全部来自你所装备的刀剑衣甲和机械义肢，而这些武具和义肢在游戏里有上百种，并且同样的一件武具在重复掉落时也有可能会带有不同的行动牌。你无需受限于自己的早期构筑选择，被迫走向某个特定流派，而是可以在获得新的武具义肢后随时更换装备以改宗换派。</p>",
